Alexa looked on as her Tag Team Partner got beat, then fucked by the rookie Grimlock. Alexa is determined to get revenge, and introduce the Rookie to the losing side of rd4.
Grimlock's debut was glorious. She downed and fucked a site favorite, and top 10 ranked wrestler her first time on the mat. Now she has her sights set on the next rank, Alexa. Did Amber just have a bad day or is the Grimlock for real?
Grimlock continues to destroy ranked wrestlers. Alexa did no better than her partner and ended up getting fucked in RD4. Grimlock is a power to reckoned with!
